OL,3,CLondon hotel manager jailed for rape
OL,4,Cand sexual assaults
OL,6,FA hotel manager has been sentenced to
OL,7,F10 years in prison, with an additional
OL,8,Fthree years on extended licence, for
OL,9,Fraping a woman and sexually assaulting
OL,10,Fthree others while working in hotels
OL,11,Facross London.
OL,13,FAhmed Fahmy, 46, of West Heath Drive
OL,14,Fin Barnet, was convicted of the
OL,15,Foffences following a two-week trial at
OL,16,FHarrow Crown Court, sitting at Hendon
OL,17,FMagistrates' Court. The jury returned
OL,18,Fguilty verdicts on one count of rape
OL,19,Fand three counts of sexual assault on
OL,20,F25 July 2024.
