OL,4,Cand sexual assaults
OL,6,FFahmy was sentenced and placed on the
OL,7,Fsex offenders' register on Wednesday,
OL,8,F23 April. As part of his sentencing,
OL,9,Fhe has also been banned from working
OL,10,Fin the hospitality industry.
OL,12,FDetectives from the Metropolitan
OL,13,FPolice believe Fahmy's offending may
OL,14,Fbe more widespread and are now
OL,15,Fappealing for any further victim-
OL,16,Fsurvivors to come forward.
