OL,6,FDetective Constable James Gomm, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation, said: "Fahmy
OL,8,Fused manipulation to abuse his
OL,9,Fposition as a hotel worker and get
OL,10,Fclose to his victims. He demonstrated
OL,11,Fa clear pattern of offending and abuse.
OL,13,F"I would also like to commend the
OL,14,Fvictim-survivors who have shared their
OL,15,Fexperience to date for the bravery
OL,16,Fthey have shown throughout the
OL,17,Finvestigation and the court
OL,18,Fproceedings.
